## Customer Order APIs

```
GET  /api/v1/orders                    # list (authenticated)
GET  /api/v1/orders/{order_number}     # detail
POST /api/v1/orders/{order_number}/cancel  # if allowed
```

Guest order lookup:

```
GET /api/v1/orders/lookup?email={email}&order_number={number}
```

Requires email verification token sent to email (prevent enumeration).

---

## Admin Order APIs

```
GET   /api/v1/admin/orders             # filter by status, date, customer
GET   /api/v1/admin/orders/{id}
PATCH /api/v1/admin/orders/{id}/status # transition with reason
POST  /api/v1/admin/orders/{id}/refund
```

Require `orders:write` permission. Audit log all admin mutations.

