## Notifications

| Event | Channel |
|-------|---------|
| OrderPlaced | Email confirmation with order summary |
| OrderShipped | Email with tracking link |
| OrderDelivered | Email (optional) |
| OrderCancelled | Email confirmation |
| OrderRefunded | Email receipt |

Templates use order snapshot data, not live catalog.

---

## Reporting Queries

Common admin reports:

- Orders by status (fulfillment queue)
- Revenue by day (`placed_at`, excluding cancelled/refunded)
- Average order value
- Top products by order line quantity

Use read replica for heavy reports (`database/04-queries`).

---

## Events

- `OrderPlaced`
- `OrderConfirmed`
- `OrderProcessing`
- `OrderShipped`
- `OrderDelivered`
- `OrderCancelled`
- `OrderRefunded`

Downstream: analytics, CRM, inventory finalization, email service.

---

## Anti-Patterns

- Mutable order lines after placement
- Deleting orders (soft cancel instead)
- Order creation without payment confirmation
- Skipping product snapshot (breaks history when catalog changes)
- Status transitions without history record
- Exposing internal database ID as customer-facing order reference
- Refund without corresponding order status update

